{"tid":1765770,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"良心公司JYP再再再再有藝人出現健康問題 一齊祝福佢","createTime":"2019-12-02T06:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T12:32:31.000Z","uid":74065,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ea184995021f2cbe9f55650f15e723063c1c6e56","tid":1765770,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"【mydaily】[GOT7王嘉爾&amp;榮宰因健康問題缺席粉絲簽名會，&quot;集中休息&quot;]GOT7成員王嘉爾和榮宰因健康原因沒有參加11月30日和12月1日舉行的粉絲簽名會。<br />\n<br />\nJYPE方面表示：&quot;王嘉爾和榮宰由於健康原因沒有參加粉絲簽名會。在進行精密檢查後，根據醫生的診斷他們需要休息，為了把藝人的健康放在第一位，讓他們集中休息，所以決定不參加粉絲簽名會。向粉絲們傳達了不參加的消息，真心地希望大家諒解。我司將盡一切努力恢復藝人的健康。&quot;<br />\n<br />\nJYP千秋千秋萬世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee036c9482653ebe1edebd163a4b844ad6021a7f","tid":1765770,"uid":46435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:30:09.000Z","msg":"嘎嘎係比人打小人打到病.."},{"pid":"0805cc4584352104f7e9960fea398d47bc3e1e19","tid":1765770,"uid":92005,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到病？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c930d3f35fa16501f680835f99dec12fd3184ea1","tid":1765770,"uid":258230,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:32:42.000Z","msg":"奶共撚自己死咗去唔好搞咁多嘢啦"},{"pid":"769c9f8de843eff54f1154bba718dbb12f6ceb0c","tid":1765770,"uid":89660,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"入咩公司可以成世唔洗病？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4769c7959f22ad79a6cb1fdf9e1b4b9d12c19d","tid":1765770,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"769c9f8de843eff54f1154bba718dbb12f6ceb0c","tid":1765770,"uid":89660,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":